[SAIKI] Looks sketchy.

495
00:16:21,333 --> 00:16:23,166
[TERUHASHI] Sounds scary.
Come on.

496
00:16:23,250 --> 00:16:24,833
[MERA] Yeah, let's look
at souvenirs.

497
